comments[6]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-07T07:30:43.392Z",claude-code-agent,"Implementation start: bundling GH-474 hybrid search --limit with GH-476 context --max-items alias in one token-efficiency PR. Duplicate checks found pm-6mn1 only covered limit=0 determinism, not general hybrid --limit parity."
  "2026-07-07T08:04:41.127Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: changed hybrid/semantic vector candidate sizing so a small --limit no longer shrinks the semantic candidate window before hybrid fusion; final output limit is still applied after sorting/fusion. Added regression coverage for --limit 1 with max_results=3 and updated extension fallback fixture to pin max_results explicitly. Verification passed: linked focused pm test (335 tests), pnpm build, node scripts/run-tests.mjs test (264 files / 5449 tests), node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage (100% statements/branches/functions/lines), pnpm typecheck, pnpm lint, pnpm security:scan, pnpm contracts:check. Packed-install dogfood in /tmp/tmp.FlmKN3LY44 confirmed installed npx pm search alpha --json --limit 1 returns filters.limit=1 and one hit. GitHub refresh found no open Dependabot security alerts; open Dependabot PRs #462/#465 remain separate dependency-update PRs and are behind base."
  "2026-07-07T08:10:58.717Z",claude-code-agent,"Greptile local review 875a3022-9652-4406-8871-7fa89c11038f found one P2 test-clarity issue: result.total=2 needed explanation in the new hybrid --limit regression. Addressed with an inline test comment explaining total is the sortable pre-truncation hybrid hit count and pm-tail falls below the mode-aware score threshold. Focused verification after fix: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/commands/search-command.spec.ts (85 tests passed)."
  "2026-07-07T08:18:31.851Z",claude-code-agent,"Greptile rerun 087e07f7-adad-40d1-92b5-eef128cedf41 completed clean after the test-comment fix. Result: confidence 5/5, safe to merge, no review comments."
  "2026-07-07T08:32:30.144Z",claude-code-agent,"Merge evidence: PR #478 (https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/pull/478) merged to main at commit 54f9145d. GitHub checks were green: CI build/runtime/coverage/static/typecheck/compat/smokes/Windows, CodeQL, CodeFactor, Greptile Review, CodeRabbit, Cubic, Codecov patch, Hound, semgrep, ShellCheck, PSScriptAnalyzer, Trivy, actionlint. Bot review threads were answered with code/test references and resolved before merge."
  "2026-07-07T08:34:55.311Z",claude-code-agent,"Post-merge closeout evidence: pnpm changelog:pm regenerated CHANGELOG.md with pm-changelog 2026.7.6 and pnpm changelog:pm:check passed; pnpm build passed; pm health --check-only --summary --json passed with telemetry/extensions/storage/locks ok; Sentry telemetry gate passed with 0 critical/high issues in the 14-day window and telemetry finish_error_rate_pct=0.58 with no missing error-code rows."
