close_reason: "Shipped in PR #478: hybrid search keeps the semantic candidate window at least max_results wide before rank fusion and applies --limit after fusion, preserving existing limit=0 determinism; focused/full coverage, Greptile local review, packed-install dogfood, and GitHub checks passed."
body: "GitHub: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/474\n\nHonor `--limit` in hybrid search mode (parity with keyword mode), applied after hybrid rank fusion so the top-N fused results are returned. Preserve the deterministic limit=0 empty-result semantics established in pm-6mn1."
